{
  "video_id": "AIfwFLDXFyQ",
  "title": "Stefano Mancuso: The roots of plant intelligence",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15260.0,
      "end_time": 18259.0,
      "text": "Sometimes I go browsing"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18260.0,
      "end_time": 20260.0,
      "text": "[through] a very old magazine."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20260.0,
      "end_time": 23260.0,
      "text": "I found this observation test"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23260.0,
      "end_time": 26260.0,
      "text": "about the story of the ark."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26260.0,
      "end_time": 29260.0,
      "text": "And the artist that drew this observation test"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29260.0,
      "end_time": 31260.0,
      "text": "did some errors, had some mistakes --"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31260.0,
      "end_time": 33260.0,
      "text": "there are more or less 12 mistakes."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 33260.0,
      "end_time": 35260.0,
      "text": "Some of them are very easy."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35260.0,
      "end_time": 38260.0,
      "text": "There is a funnel, an aerial part,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38260.0,
      "end_time": 40260.0,
      "text": "a lamp and clockwork key on the ark."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40260.0,
      "end_time": 43260.0,
      "text": "Some of them are about the animals, the number."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 43260.0,
      "end_time": 46260.0,
      "text": "But there is a much more fundamental mistake"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 46260.0,
      "end_time": 49260.0,
      "text": "in the overall story of the ark"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 49260.0,
      "end_time": 51260.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s not reported here."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 51260.0,
      "end_time": 54260.0,
      "text": "And this problem is: where are the plants?"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 54260.0,
      "end_time": 56260.0,
      "text": "So now we have God"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 56260.0,
      "end_time": 59260.0,
      "text": "that is going to submerge Earth permanently"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 59260.0,
      "end_time": 62260.0,
      "text": "or at least for a very long period,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 62260.0,
      "end_time": 65259.0,
      "text": "and no one is taking care of plants."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 65260.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67260.0,
      "text": "Noah needed to take two of every kind of bird,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 67260.0,
      "end_time": 69260.0,
      "text": "of every kind of animal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 69260.0,
      "end_time": 71260.0,
      "text": "of every kind of creature that moves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 71260.0,
      "end_time": 74260.0,
      "text": "but no mention about plants."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 74260.0,
      "end_time": 76260.0,
      "text": "Why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 76260.0,
      "end_time": 78260.0,
      "text": "In another part of the same story,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 78260.0,
      "end_time": 80260.0,
      "text": "all the living creatures"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 80260.0,
      "end_time": 82260.0,
      "text": "are just the living creatures"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 82260.0,
      "end_time": 84260.0,
      "text": "that came out from the ark,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 84260.0,
      "end_time": 87260.0,
      "text": "so birds, livestock and wild animals."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 87260.0,
      "end_time": 89260.0,
      "text": "Plants are not living creatures --"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 89260.0,
      "end_time": 91260.0,
      "text": "this is the point."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 91260.0,
      "end_time": 93260.0,
      "text": "That is a point that is not"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 93260.0,
      "end_time": 95260.0,
      "text": "coming out from the Bible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 95260.0,
      "end_time": 97260.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s something that"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 97260.0,
      "end_time": 100260.0,
      "text": "really accompanied humanity."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 100260.0,
      "end_time": 103260.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s have a look at this nice code"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 103260.0,
      "end_time": 106260.0,
      "text": "that is coming from a Renaissance book."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 106260.0,
      "end_time": 108260.0,
      "text": "Here we have the description"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 108260.0,
      "end_time": 110260.0,
      "text": "of the order of nature."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 110260.0,
      "end_time": 113260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a nice description because it&#39;s starting from left --"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 113260.0,
      "end_time": 115260.0,
      "text": "you have the stones --"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 115260.0,
      "end_time": 117260.0,
      "text": "immediately after the stones, the plants"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 117260.0,
      "end_time": 120260.0,
      "text": "that are just able to live."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 120260.0,
      "end_time": 123260.0,
      "text": "We have the animals that are able to live and to sense,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 123260.0,
      "end_time": 125260.0,
      "text": "and on the top of the pyramid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 125260.0,
      "end_time": 127260.0,
      "text": "there is the man."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 127260.0,
      "end_time": 129259.0,
      "text": "This is not the common man."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 129258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 132260.0,
      "text": "The \"Homo studiosus\" -- the studying man."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 132260.0,
      "end_time": 135260.0,
      "text": "This is quite comforting"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 135260.0,
      "end_time": 138260.0,
      "text": "for people like me -- I&#39;m a professor --"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 138260.0,
      "end_time": 141260.0,
      "text": "this to be over there on the top of creation."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 141260.0,
      "end_time": 144260.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s something completely wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 144260.0,
      "end_time": 147260.0,
      "text": "You know very well about professors."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 147260.0,
      "end_time": 150260.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s also wrong about plants,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 150260.0,
      "end_time": 152260.0,
      "text": "because plants are not just able to live;"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 152260.0,
      "end_time": 154260.0,
      "text": "they are able to sense."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 154260.0,
      "end_time": 156260.0,
      "text": "They are much more sophisticated"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 156260.0,
      "end_time": 158260.0,
      "text": "in sensing than animals."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 158260.0,
      "end_time": 160260.0,
      "text": "Just to give you an example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 160260.0,
      "end_time": 162260.0,
      "text": "every single root apex"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 162260.0,
      "end_time": 165260.0,
      "text": "is able to detect and to monitor"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 165260.0,
      "end_time": 167260.0,
      "text": "concurrently and continuously"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 167260.0,
      "end_time": 169260.0,
      "text": "at least 15 different chemical"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 169260.0,
      "end_time": 172260.0,
      "text": "and physical parameters."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 172260.0,
      "end_time": 175260.0,
      "text": "And they also are able to show and to exhibit"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 175260.0,
      "end_time": 178260.0,
      "text": "such a wonderful and complex behavior"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 178260.0,
      "end_time": 181260.0,
      "text": "that can be described just with the term of intelligence."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 181260.0,
      "end_time": 184260.0,
      "text": "Well, but this is something --"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 184260.0,
      "end_time": 186260.0,
      "text": "this underestimation of plants is something"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 186260.0,
      "end_time": 189260.0,
      "text": "that is always with us."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 189260.0,
      "end_time": 192260.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s have a look at this short movie now."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 192260.0,
      "end_time": 194260.0,
      "text": "We have David Attenborough."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 194260.0,
      "end_time": 196260.0,
      "text": "Now David Attenborough is really a plant lover;"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 196260.0,
      "end_time": 199260.0,
      "text": "he did some of the most beautiful movies"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 199260.0,
      "end_time": 201260.0,
      "text": "about plant behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 201260.0,
      "end_time": 203260.0,
      "text": "Now, when he speaks about plants,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 203260.0,
      "end_time": 205260.0,
      "text": "everything is correct."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 205260.0,
      "end_time": 207260.0,
      "text": "When he speaks about animals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 207260.0,
      "end_time": 209260.0,
      "text": "[he] tends to remove the fact"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 209260.0,
      "end_time": 211260.0,
      "text": "that plants exist."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 211260.0,
      "end_time": 213260.0,
      "text": "The blue whale,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 213260.0,
      "end_time": 215260.0,
      "text": "the biggest creature that exists on the planet --"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 215260.0,
      "end_time": 218260.0,
      "text": "that is wrong, completely wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 218260.0,
      "end_time": 221260.0,
      "text": "The blue whale, it&#39;s a dwarf"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 221260.0,
      "end_time": 223260.0,
      "text": "if compared with the real biggest creature"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 223260.0,
      "end_time": 225260.0,
      "text": "that exists on the planet --"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 225260.0,
      "end_time": 227260.0,
      "text": "that is, this wonderful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 227260.0,
      "end_time": 231260.0,
      "text": "magnificent Sequoiadendron giganteum."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 231260.0,
      "end_time": 233260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 233260.0,
      "end_time": 236260.0,
      "text": "And this is a living organism"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 236260.0,
      "end_time": 239260.0,
      "text": "that has a mass of at least 2,000 tons."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 239260.0,
      "end_time": 241260.0,
      "text": "Now, the story"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 241260.0,
      "end_time": 244260.0,
      "text": "that plants are some low-level organisms"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 244260.0,
      "end_time": 247260.0,
      "text": "has been formalized"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 247260.0,
      "end_time": 250260.0,
      "text": "many times ago by Aristotle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 250260.0,
      "end_time": 252260.0,
      "text": "that in \"De Anima\" --"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 252260.0,
      "end_time": 255260.0,
      "text": "that is a very influential book for the Western civilization --"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 255260.0,
      "end_time": 258260.0,
      "text": "wrote that the plants are on the edge"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 258260.0,
      "end_time": 261260.0,
      "text": "between living and not living."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 261260.0,
      "end_time": 264260.0,
      "text": "They have just a kind of very low-level soul."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 264260.0,
      "end_time": 267260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s called the vegetative soul,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 267260.0,
      "end_time": 270260.0,
      "text": "because they lack movement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 270260.0,
      "end_time": 272260.0,
      "text": "and so they don&#39;t need to sense."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 272260.0,
      "end_time": 274260.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s see."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 274260.0,
      "end_time": 277260.0,
      "text": "Okay, some of the movements of the plants are very well-known."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 277260.0,
      "end_time": 279260.0,
      "text": "This is a very fast movement."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 279260.0,
      "end_time": 282260.0,
      "text": "This is a Dionaea, a Venus fly trap"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 282260.0,
      "end_time": 284260.0,
      "text": "hunting snails --"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 284260.0,
      "end_time": 286260.0,
      "text": "sorry for the snail."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 286260.0,
      "end_time": 289260.0,
      "text": "This has been something that has been refused for centuries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 289260.0,
      "end_time": 292260.0,
      "text": "despite the evidence."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 292260.0,
      "end_time": 295260.0,
      "text": "No one can say that the plants were able to eat an animal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 295260.0,
      "end_time": 298260.0,
      "text": "because it was against the order of nature."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 298260.0,
      "end_time": 300260.0,
      "text": "But plants are also able"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 300260.0,
      "end_time": 303260.0,
      "text": "to show a lot of movement."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 303260.0,
      "end_time": 306260.0,
      "text": "Some of them are very well known, like the flowering."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 306260.0,
      "end_time": 309260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s just a question to use some techniques"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 309260.0,
      "end_time": 311260.0,
      "text": "like the time lapse."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 311260.0,
      "end_time": 314260.0,
      "text": "Some of them are much more sophisticated."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 314260.0,
      "end_time": 316260.0,
      "text": "Look at this young bean"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 316260.0,
      "end_time": 319260.0,
      "text": "that is moving to catch the light every time."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 319260.0,
      "end_time": 321260.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s really so graceful;"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 321260.0,
      "end_time": 324260.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s like a dancing angel."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 324260.0,
      "end_time": 327260.0,
      "text": "They are also able to play --"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 327260.0,
      "end_time": 329260.0,
      "text": "they are really playing."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 329260.0,
      "end_time": 332260.0,
      "text": "These are young sunflowers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 332260.0,
      "end_time": 334260.0,
      "text": "and what they are doing"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 334260.0,
      "end_time": 336260.0,
      "text": "cannot be described"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 336260.0,
      "end_time": 338260.0,
      "text": "with any other terms than playing."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 338260.0,
      "end_time": 340260.0,
      "text": "They are training themselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 340260.0,
      "end_time": 342260.0,
      "text": "as many young animals do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 342260.0,
      "end_time": 344260.0,
      "text": "to the adult life"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 344260.0,
      "end_time": 347260.0,
      "text": "where they will be called to track the sun"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 347260.0,
      "end_time": 349260.0,
      "text": "all the day."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 349260.0,
      "end_time": 352260.0,
      "text": "They are able to respond to gravity, of course,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 352260.0,
      "end_time": 354260.0,
      "text": "so the shoots are growing"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 354260.0,
      "end_time": 356260.0,
      "text": "against the vector of gravity"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 356260.0,
      "end_time": 359260.0,
      "text": "and the roots toward the vector of gravity."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 359260.0,
      "end_time": 362260.0,
      "text": "But they are also able to sleep."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 362260.0,
      "end_time": 364260.0,
      "text": "This is one, Mimosa pudica."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 364260.0,
      "end_time": 366260.0,
      "text": "So during the night,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 366260.0,
      "end_time": 368260.0,
      "text": "they curl the leaves"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 368260.0,
      "end_time": 370260.0,
      "text": "and reduce the movement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 370260.0,
      "end_time": 372260.0,
      "text": "and during the day, you have the opening of the leaves --"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 372260.0,
      "end_time": 374260.0,
      "text": "there is much more movement."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 374260.0,
      "end_time": 376260.0,
      "text": "This is interesting"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 376260.0,
      "end_time": 378260.0,
      "text": "because this sleeping machinery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 378260.0,
      "end_time": 380260.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s perfectly conserved."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 380260.0,
      "end_time": 382260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the same in plants, in insects"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 382260.0,
      "end_time": 384260.0,
      "text": "and in animals."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 384260.0,
      "end_time": 387260.0,
      "text": "And so if you need to study this sleeping problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 387260.0,
      "end_time": 390260.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s easy to study on plants, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 390260.0,
      "end_time": 392260.0,
      "text": "than in animals"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 392260.0,
      "end_time": 395260.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s much more easy even ethically."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 395260.0,
      "end_time": 398260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a kind of vegetarian"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 398260.0,
      "end_time": 400260.0,
      "text": "experimentation."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 400260.0,
      "end_time": 403260.0,
      "text": "Plants are even able to communicate --"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 403260.0,
      "end_time": 405260.0,
      "text": "they are extraordinary communicators."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 405260.0,
      "end_time": 407260.0,
      "text": "They communicate with other plants."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 407260.0,
      "end_time": 410260.0,
      "text": "They are able to distinguish kin and non-kin."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 410260.0,
      "end_time": 412260.0,
      "text": "They communicate"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 412260.0,
      "end_time": 414260.0,
      "text": "with plants of other species"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 414260.0,
      "end_time": 416260.0,
      "text": "and they communicate with animals"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 416260.0,
      "end_time": 419260.0,
      "text": "by producing chemical volatiles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 419260.0,
      "end_time": 421260.0,
      "text": "for example, during the pollination."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 421260.0,
      "end_time": 424260.0,
      "text": "Now with the pollination, it&#39;s a very serious issue for plants,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 424260.0,
      "end_time": 427260.0,
      "text": "because they move the pollen from one flower to the other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 427260.0,
      "end_time": 429260.0,
      "text": "yet they cannot move from one flower to the other."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 429260.0,
      "end_time": 431260.0,
      "text": "So they need a vector --"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 431260.0,
      "end_time": 433260.0,
      "text": "and this vector,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 433260.0,
      "end_time": 435260.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s normally an animal."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 435260.0,
      "end_time": 437260.0,
      "text": "Many insects"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 437260.0,
      "end_time": 440260.0,
      "text": "have been used by plants as vectors"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 440260.0,
      "end_time": 442260.0,
      "text": "for the transport of the pollination,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 442260.0,
      "end_time": 445260.0,
      "text": "but not just insects; even birds, reptiles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 445260.0,
      "end_time": 448260.0,
      "text": "and mammals like bats rats"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 448260.0,
      "end_time": 451260.0,
      "text": "are normally used for the transportation of the pollen."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 451260.0,
      "end_time": 453260.0,
      "text": "This is a serious business."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 453260.0,
      "end_time": 456260.0,
      "text": "We have the plants that are giving to the animals"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 456260.0,
      "end_time": 459260.0,
      "text": "a kind of sweet substance --"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 459260.0,
      "end_time": 461260.0,
      "text": "very energizing --"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 461260.0,
      "end_time": 464260.0,
      "text": "having in change this transportation of the pollen."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 464260.0,
      "end_time": 467260.0,
      "text": "But some plants are manipulating animals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 467260.0,
      "end_time": 469260.0,
      "text": "like in the case of orchids"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 469260.0,
      "end_time": 471260.0,
      "text": "that promise sex and nectar"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 471260.0,
      "end_time": 473260.0,
      "text": "and give in change nothing"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 473260.0,
      "end_time": 476260.0,
      "text": "for the transportation of the pollen."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 476260.0,
      "end_time": 479260.0,
      "text": "Now, there is a big problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 479260.0,
      "end_time": 482260.0,
      "text": "behind all this behavior that we have seen."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 482260.0,
      "end_time": 485260.0,
      "text": "How is it possible to do this without a brain?"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 485260.0,
      "end_time": 488260.0,
      "text": "We need to wait until 1880,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 488260.0,
      "end_time": 490260.0,
      "text": "when this big man,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 490260.0,
      "end_time": 492260.0,
      "text": "Charles Darwin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 492260.0,
      "end_time": 495260.0,
      "text": "publishes a wonderful, astonishing book"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 495260.0,
      "end_time": 498260.0,
      "text": "that starts a revolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 498260.0,
      "end_time": 501260.0,
      "text": "The title is \"The Power of Movement in Plants.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 501260.0,
      "end_time": 503260.0,
      "text": "No one was allowed to speak about movement in plants"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 503260.0,
      "end_time": 505260.0,
      "text": "before Charles Darwin."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 505260.0,
      "end_time": 507260.0,
      "text": "In his book,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 507260.0,
      "end_time": 509260.0,
      "text": "assisted by his son, Francis --"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 509260.0,
      "end_time": 512260.0,
      "text": "who was the first professor of plant physiology in the world, in Cambridge --"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 512260.0,
      "end_time": 515260.0,
      "text": "they took into consideration every single movement"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 515260.0,
      "end_time": 517260.0,
      "text": "for 500 pages."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 517260.0,
      "end_time": 520260.0,
      "text": "And in the last paragraph of the book,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 520260.0,
      "end_time": 522260.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s a kind of stylistic mark,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 522260.0,
      "end_time": 525260.0,
      "text": "because normally Charles Darwin stored,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 525260.0,
      "end_time": 527260.0,
      "text": "in the last paragraph of a book,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 527260.0,
      "end_time": 529260.0,
      "text": "the most important message."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 529260.0,
      "end_time": 531260.0,
      "text": "He wrote that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 531260.0,
      "end_time": 533260.0,
      "text": "\"It&#39;s hardly an exaggeration"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 533260.0,
      "end_time": 536260.0,
      "text": "to say that the tip of the radical"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 536260.0,
      "end_time": 538260.0,
      "text": "acts like the brain"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 538260.0,
      "end_time": 540260.0,
      "text": "of one of the lower animals.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 540260.0,
      "end_time": 542260.0,
      "text": "This is not a metaphor."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 542260.0,
      "end_time": 545260.0,
      "text": "He wrote some very interesting letters to one of his friends"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 545260.0,
      "end_time": 549260.0,
      "text": "who was J.D. Hooker, or at that time, president of the Royal Society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 549260.0,
      "end_time": 552260.0,
      "text": "so the maximum scientific authority in Britain"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 552260.0,
      "end_time": 555260.0,
      "text": "speaking about the brain in the plants."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 555260.0,
      "end_time": 557260.0,
      "text": "Now, this is a root apex"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 557260.0,
      "end_time": 559260.0,
      "text": "growing against a slope."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 559260.0,
      "end_time": 562260.0,
      "text": "So you can recognize this kind of movement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 562260.0,
      "end_time": 565260.0,
      "text": "the same movement that worms, snakes"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 565260.0,
      "end_time": 567260.0,
      "text": "and every animal"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 567260.0,
      "end_time": 570260.0,
      "text": "that are moving on the ground without legs"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 570260.0,
      "end_time": 572260.0,
      "text": "is able to display."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 572260.0,
      "end_time": 574260.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s not an easy movement"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 574260.0,
      "end_time": 577260.0,
      "text": "because, to have this kind of movement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 577260.0,
      "end_time": 580260.0,
      "text": "you need to move different regions of the root"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 580260.0,
      "end_time": 582260.0,
      "text": "and to synchronize these different regions"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 582260.0,
      "end_time": 584260.0,
      "text": "without having a brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 584260.0,
      "end_time": 587260.0,
      "text": "So we studied the root apex"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 587260.0,
      "end_time": 589260.0,
      "text": "and we found that there is a specific region"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 589260.0,
      "end_time": 592260.0,
      "text": "that is here, depicted in blue --"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 592260.0,
      "end_time": 594260.0,
      "text": "that is called the \"transition zone.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 594260.0,
      "end_time": 597260.0,
      "text": "And this region, it&#39;s a very small region --"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 597260.0,
      "end_time": 600260.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s less than one millimeter."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 600260.0,
      "end_time": 602260.0,
      "text": "And in this small region"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 602260.0,
      "end_time": 604260.0,
      "text": "you have the highest consumption"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 604260.0,
      "end_time": 606260.0,
      "text": "of oxygen in the plants"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 606260.0,
      "end_time": 608260.0,
      "text": "and more important,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 608260.0,
      "end_time": 610260.0,
      "text": "you have these kinds of signals here."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 610260.0,
      "end_time": 613260.0,
      "text": "The signals that you are seeing here are action potential,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 613260.0,
      "end_time": 615260.0,
      "text": "are the same signals"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 615260.0,
      "end_time": 618260.0,
      "text": "that the neurons of my brain, of our brain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 618260.0,
      "end_time": 621260.0,
      "text": "use to exchange information."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 621260.0,
      "end_time": 624260.0,
      "text": "Now we know that a root apex"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 624260.0,
      "end_time": 626260.0,
      "text": "has just a few hundred cells"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 626260.0,
      "end_time": 628260.0,
      "text": "that show this kind of feature,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 628260.0,
      "end_time": 630260.0,
      "text": "but we know how big"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 630260.0,
      "end_time": 633260.0,
      "text": "the root apparatus of a small plant, like a plant of rye."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 633260.0,
      "end_time": 635260.0,
      "text": "We have almost"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 635260.0,
      "end_time": 637260.0,
      "text": "14 million roots."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 637260.0,
      "end_time": 640260.0,
      "text": "We have 11 and a half million"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 640260.0,
      "end_time": 642260.0,
      "text": "root apex"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 642260.0,
      "end_time": 645260.0,
      "text": "and a total length of 600 or more kilometers"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 645260.0,
      "end_time": 647260.0,
      "text": "and a very high surface area."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 647260.0,
      "end_time": 649260.0,
      "text": "Now let&#39;s imagine"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 649260.0,
      "end_time": 651260.0,
      "text": "that each single root apex"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 651260.0,
      "end_time": 654260.0,
      "text": "is working in network with all the others."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 654260.0,
      "end_time": 657260.0,
      "text": "Here were have on the left, the Internet"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 657260.0,
      "end_time": 660260.0,
      "text": "and on the right, the root apparatus."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 660260.0,
      "end_time": 662260.0,
      "text": "They work in the same way."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 662260.0,
      "end_time": 664260.0,
      "text": "They are a network"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 664260.0,
      "end_time": 666260.0,
      "text": "of small computing machines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 666260.0,
      "end_time": 668260.0,
      "text": "working in networks."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 668260.0,
      "end_time": 670260.0,
      "text": "And why are they so similar?"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 670260.0,
      "end_time": 672260.0,
      "text": "Because they evolved"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 672260.0,
      "end_time": 674260.0,
      "text": "for the same reason:"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 674260.0,
      "end_time": 677260.0,
      "text": "to survive predation."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 677260.0,
      "end_time": 679260.0,
      "text": "They work in the same way."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 679260.0,
      "end_time": 682260.0,
      "text": "So you can remove 90 percent of the root apparatus"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 682260.0,
      "end_time": 684260.0,
      "text": "and the plants [continue] to work."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 684260.0,
      "end_time": 687260.0,
      "text": "You can remove 90 percent of the Internet"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 687260.0,
      "end_time": 690260.0,
      "text": "and it is [continuing] to work."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 690260.0,
      "end_time": 692260.0,
      "text": "So, a suggestion"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 692260.0,
      "end_time": 695260.0,
      "text": "for the people working with networks:"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 695260.0,
      "end_time": 698260.0,
      "text": "plants are able"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 698260.0,
      "end_time": 700260.0,
      "text": "to give you good suggestions"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 700260.0,
      "end_time": 703260.0,
      "text": "about how to evolve networks."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 703260.0,
      "end_time": 706260.0,
      "text": "And another possibility"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 706260.0,
      "end_time": 709260.0,
      "text": "is a technological possibility."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 709260.0,
      "end_time": 711260.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s imagine"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 711260.0,
      "end_time": 713260.0,
      "text": "that we can build robots"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 713260.0,
      "end_time": 716260.0,
      "text": "and robots that are inspired by plants."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 716260.0,
      "end_time": 718260.0,
      "text": "Until now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 718260.0,
      "end_time": 721260.0,
      "text": "the man was inspired"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 721260.0,
      "end_time": 723260.0,
      "text": "just by man or the animals"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 723260.0,
      "end_time": 725260.0,
      "text": "in producing a robot."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 725260.0,
      "end_time": 728260.0,
      "text": "We have the animaloid --"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 728260.0,
      "end_time": 730260.0,
      "text": "and the normal robots inspired by animals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 730260.0,
      "end_time": 732260.0,
      "text": "insectoid, so on."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 732260.0,
      "end_time": 734260.0,
      "text": "We have the androids"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 734260.0,
      "end_time": 737260.0,
      "text": "that are inspired by man."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 737260.0,
      "end_time": 740260.0,
      "text": "But why have we not any plantoid?"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 740260.0,
      "end_time": 742260.0,
      "text": "Well, if you want to fly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 742260.0,
      "end_time": 744260.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s good that you look at birds --"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 744260.0,
      "end_time": 746260.0,
      "text": "to be inspired by birds."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 746260.0,
      "end_time": 749260.0,
      "text": "But if you want to explore soils,"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 749260.0,
      "end_time": 752260.0,
      "text": "or if you want to colonize"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 752260.0,
      "end_time": 754260.0,
      "text": "new territory,"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 754260.0,
      "end_time": 757260.0,
      "text": "to best thing that you can do is to be inspired by plants"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 757260.0,
      "end_time": 760260.0,
      "text": "that are masters in doing this."
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 760260.0,
      "end_time": 762260.0,
      "text": "We have another possibility"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 762260.0,
      "end_time": 764260.0,
      "text": "we are working [on] in our lab,"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 764260.0,
      "end_time": 766260.0,
      "text": "[which] is to build hybrids."
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 766260.0,
      "end_time": 769260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s much more easy to build hybrids."
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 769260.0,
      "end_time": 771260.0,
      "text": "Hybrid means it&#39;s something"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 771260.0,
      "end_time": 774260.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s half living and half machine."
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 774260.0,
      "end_time": 776260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s much more easy to work with plants"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 776260.0,
      "end_time": 778260.0,
      "text": "than with animals."
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 778260.0,
      "end_time": 780260.0,
      "text": "They have computing power,"
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 780260.0,
      "end_time": 782260.0,
      "text": "they have electrical signals."
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 782260.0,
      "end_time": 785260.0,
      "text": "The connection with the machine is much more easy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 785260.0,
      "end_time": 789260.0,
      "text": "much more even ethically possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 790260.0,
      "end_time": 792260.0,
      "text": "And these are three possibilities"
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 792260.0,
      "end_time": 795260.0,
      "text": "that we are working on"
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 795260.0,
      "end_time": 797260.0,
      "text": "to build hybrids,"
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 797260.0,
      "end_time": 799260.0,
      "text": "driven by algae"
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 799260.0,
      "end_time": 802260.0,
      "text": "or by the leaves at the end,"
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 802260.0,
      "end_time": 804260.0,
      "text": "by the most, most powerful parts of the plants,"
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "start_time": 804260.0,
      "end_time": 806260.0,
      "text": "by the roots."
    },
    {
      "index": 322,
      "start_time": 806260.0,
      "end_time": 808260.0,
      "text": "Well, thank you for your attention."
    },
    {
      "index": 323,
      "start_time": 808260.0,
      "end_time": 811260.0,
      "text": "And before I finish,"
    },
    {
      "index": 324,
      "start_time": 811260.0,
      "end_time": 814260.0,
      "text": "I would like to reassure that no snails were harmed"
    },
    {
      "index": 325,
      "start_time": 814260.0,
      "end_time": 816260.0,
      "text": "in making this presentation."
    },
    {
      "index": 326,
      "start_time": 816260.0,
      "end_time": 818260.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 327,
      "start_time": 818260.0,
      "end_time": 823260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}